    <h2 id="weights">Weights</h2>
    <p>Use Frutiger Regular for body text.</p>
    <p class="rich-text"><code>font-weight: 400;</code></p>
    <p>Use <strong>Frutiger Regular Bold</strong> for headings and emphasis.</p>
    <p class="rich-text"><code>font-weight: 600;</code></p>
    <h2 id="research">Research</h2>
    <p>We've tested our typography with lots of users including, for example, people with dyslexia and colour blindness.</p>
    <div class="nhsuk-review-date">
    <p class="nhsuk-body-s">Updated: January 2019</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
